{"tid":1412150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［愛國愛港］我地要配合政府施政，發起全港超合作運動！","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:21:31.000Z","uid":283166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad2d820bd6ef810650057ba5fba2b47c06d4ffd","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"無錯，我係Ｐ牌<br />\n<br />\n睇完頭先民主女神林太的記召，實在深受感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一定要配合政府施政，<br />\n發動超合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然香港人咁鍾意返工，我地要諗諗辦法幫幫佢地手<br />\n但諗還諗，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家千祈唔好檔住Ｄ闊閘機的入閘位呀</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果唔係打工就無得享受用八達通聽嘟一聲的樂趣，自由入閘會令港鐵收唔倒票錢，影響好大架<br />\n<br />\n最近大家搞隧道，對駕車人仕實在有太大的影響啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家千祈千祈唔好整壞個收費閘口呀</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，駕車人仕直行直過的話，隧道收唔到錢點算呀<br />\n<br />\n大家要做的，就要幫助政府施政，政府機構的傳單要幫手派發，成日擺係個架度市民點會收到傳單的資訊呀，咁政府先可以再印一批新的派發嘛<br />\n<br />\n為左令各區的居民知道區議會用左Ｄ錢係邊度，一定要幫Ｄ設施標返個價錢上去，如果唔係市民點知道政府放左幾多心機係地區工作上面呀<br />\n你睇一百毛訪問就知街坊有幾唔了解政府的一翻心機啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tvmost.com.hk/201610201128_video_loverewind_mylittleelephant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2F201610201128_video_loverewind_mylittleelephant&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWIVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=8a80c4f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tvmost.com.hk/201610201128_video_loverewind_mylittleelephant</a><br />\n<br />\n但記得呀，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好搞智能燈柱呀</strong></span>，政府唔想比人知燈柱攞尼做咩架，所以唔好貼燈柱的說明書係上面呀，你地之前已經搞過交通燈，唔好再搞燈柱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲有無諗到點樣可以幫到政府施政又幫到市民的行動呀？"},{"pid":"deff81100959cf26a7e2f76200238a014fc02ac3","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3a6fac48d729919dae06a62ab0d4c2afa006a47","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"56cdd24fa2ab1a05bb817c38cfdee7845eeef6e5","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"我好中意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a0ca75306091e16172d72abf09d2c852eda754","tid":1412150,"uid":97603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"收費閘口有cam 好似唔比錢都會比人追"},{"pid":"ff75959699daf05001e75f0abaa266bf0ab979f1","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28a0ca75306091e16172d72abf09d2c852eda754","tid":1412150,"uid":97603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"收費閘口有cam 好似唔比錢都會比人追"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"個ＣＡＭ有無得諗諗佢呀？"},{"pid":"e1558cef8494b981e90c3db4bcb2adaa4190a2e4","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:46:36.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港"},{"pid":"78410deff816d3ddcde2621d03a871d3f35d8a79","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"我好中意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8531ce5249cd575d1b45c4f08541cead89e10b38","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"我好中意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050ea1e4ea35cc6bb697b7fe39916a8d14b72da0","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"我好中意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061ef0686b90274a08fa4874e91893c03c856408","tid":1412150,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc